#                                                  THREE-LANGUAGE SYMMETRY
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# With this completion the cross-language CLI library taxonomy documents
# the 70TH TypeScript-Node CLI library variant.  TS-Node climbs from 69
# to 70 documented libraries (got via liara).  TS-Node **catches Rust
# AND Go at 70** (Rust=Go=TS-Node=70 → second three-way tie at the
